    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292480/extras/2c4acca241be987ea3b1e130491c42e6.poster.avif?t=1758140419\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292480/extras/2c4acca241be987ea3b1e130491c42e6.webm?t=1758140419\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292480/extras/2c4acca241be987ea3b1e130491c42e6.mp4?t=1758140419\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You abandoned your old life as a firefighter, fleeing from the tormenting memories of a family you couldn't save from a house fire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But why do you feel like something isn't right?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What is that noise? And why do I feel like it's calling me back to the house?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The deeper you venture into the shadows, the more you begin to question.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Is there someone waiting for me beyond the afterlife?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292480/extras/04ebf524679b7723760b2665b19d42dd.poster.avif?t=1758140419\" width=800 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292480/extras/04ebf524679b7723760b2665b19d42dd.webm?t=1758140419\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ignited Entry is a full length narrative driven psychological horror game with voice acting, dreamish visuals, and horror elements that will keep you on the edge of your seat. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Some doors should never be opened. But you must go in.</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292480/extras/c68bfb9a307ca7137a620e92762073f4.avif?t=1758140419\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292480/extras_big/c68bfb9a307ca7137a620e92762073f4.avif?t=1758140419 width=800 height=88 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Voice Acting</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Full Length Play Session</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Full Story</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Progress Saving Level Jumping</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292480/extras/66c9a8ae3d85325479bbedd5b6ee51b6.avif?t=1758140419\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292480/extras_big/66c9a8ae3d85325479bbedd5b6ee51b6.avif?t=1758140419 width=800 height=91 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8-BitRyan</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hollow</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TUV</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SWOL</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cyccubus</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >That Plush</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jordan Lindgren</p></li></ul>",
